      "side": 1,
      "message": "We’ve purged Crashpad of old-style typedefs. Now we use new-style using:\n\nusing ScopedBufferPtr \u003d std::unique_ptr\u003cchar*, BufferFreer\u003e;\n\nSome people find the new style more readable, because the \u003d helps the reader know which side is the new type and which is the existing type.",
